(https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Woven_fabric)"""@en ;
                                                        rdfs:label "Woven textile"@en .


###  https://w3id.org/simat/YieldStrength
<https://w3id.org/simat/YieldStrength> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                         rdfs:subClassOf <https://w3id.org/simat/PlasticProperty> ,
                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
