om-2:Depth rdf:type owl:Class ;
           rdfs:subClassOf om-2:Length ;
           om-2:symbol "d" ;
           rdfs:label "depth"@en ,
                      "diepte"@nl .


###  http://www.ontology-of-units-of-measure.org/resource/om-2/Diameter
