(http://purl.allotrope.org/ontologies/quality#AFQ_0000341)"""@en ;
                         rdfs:label "elasticiteitsmodulus"@nl ,
                                    "modulus of elasticity"@en ;
                         skos:altLabel "Young’s modulus"@en .


###  http://www.ontology-of-units-of-measure.org/resource/om-2/MomentOfForce
