###  https://w3id.org/simat/TestPyramideLevel
:TestPyramideLevel rdf:type owl:Class ;
                   rdfs:comment """A programme of analysis through experimental testing using specimens of various size, geometry and complexity to certify complex aero-structures. The process utilises a so-called 'building block' or 'testing pyramid' approach with tests at each of the following levels: (i) Coupon, (ii) Structural detail, (iii) Component, and (iv) Sub-structure or full structure.
(https://researchportal.bath.ac.uk/en/projects/re-shaping-the-test-pyramid)"""@en ;
                   rdfs:label "Test pyramide level"@en .


