terms:accrualMethod terms:description "Recommended practice is to use a value from the Collection Description Accrual Method Vocabulary [[DCMI-ACCRUALMETHOD](https://dublincore.org/groups/collections/accrual-method/)]."@en ;
                    terms:issued "2005-06-13"^^xsd:date ;
                    rdfs:comment "The method by which items are added to a collection."@en ;
                    rdfs:isDefinedBy terms: ;
                    rdfs:label "Accrual Method"@en .


terms:accrualPeriodicity terms:description "Recommended practice is to use a value from the Collection Description Frequency Vocabulary [[DCMI-COLLFREQ](https://dublincore.org/groups/collections/frequency/)]."@en ;
                         terms:issued "2005-06-13"^^xsd:date ;
                         rdfs:comment "The frequency with which items are added to a collection."@en ;
                         rdfs:isDefinedBy terms: ;
                         rdfs:label "Accrual Periodicity"@en .


terms:accrualPolicy terms:description "Recommended practice is to use a value from the Collection Description Accrual Policy Vocabulary [[DCMI-ACCRUALPOLICY](https://dublincore.org/groups/collections/accrual-policy/)]."@en ;
                    terms:issued "2005-06-13"^^xsd:date ;
                    rdfs:comment "The policy governing the addition of items to a collection."@en ;
                    rdfs:isDefinedBy terms: ;
                    rdfs:label "Accrual Policy"@en .


terms:alternative terms:description "The distinction between titles and alternative titles is application-specific."@en ;
                  terms:issued "2000-07-11"^^xsd:date ;
                  rdfs:comment "An alternative name for the resource."@en ;
                  rdfs:isDefinedBy terms: ;
                  rdfs:label "Alternative Title"@en .


terms:audience terms:description "Recommended practice is to use this property with non-literal values from a vocabulary of audience types."@en ;
               terms:issued "2001-05-21"^^xsd:date ;
               rdfs:comment "A class of agents for whom the resource is intended or useful."@en ;
               rdfs:isDefinedBy terms: ;
               rdfs:label "Audience"@en .


terms:available terms:description "Recommended practice is to describe the date, date/time, or period of time as recommended for the property Date, of which this is a subproperty."@en ;
                terms:issued "2000-07-11"^^xsd:date ;
                rdfs:comment "Date that the resource became or will become available."@en ;
                rdfs:isDefinedBy terms: ;
                rdfs:label "Date Available"@en .


terms:bibliographicCitation terms:description "Recommended practice is to include sufficient bibliographic detail to identify the resource as unambiguously as possible."@en ;
