terms:rights terms:description "Typically, rights information includes a statement about various property rights associated with the resource, including intellectual property rights.  Recommended practice is to refer to a rights statement with a URI.  If this is not possible or feasible, a literal value (name, label, or short text) may be provided."@en ;
